articles.description: Russia staged its largest missile attack in weeks on Kyiv and the surrounding region on Thursday, injuring at least 17 people and damaging schools, residential buildings and industrial facilities, officials said.
articles.title: In pictures: Russia launches largest missile attack on Kyiv in weeks

articles.title: On the perilous streets of Haiti
